
Basic Operations in SQLite :

1. Open SQLite session in terminal
        
        $ sqlite3 /path/to/db_filename.db


2. Create a Table

        $ create table table_name( var_name var_type(size),....);
        
        # an example
        $ create table tab00(id smallint, desc varchar(20));


3. Display a Table's contents

        $ select * from table_name;


4. Insert into Table

        $ insert into table_name values(value00,value01,....);

        # an example
        $ insert into tab00 values(2, 'description for 2');


